Will there be parking provided?

There is ample private car parking facilities available at the wooltower.

are taxis available from the venue?

Yes, there are a number of taxi companies in ballymena to choose from. it is essential to pre-book your taxi in advance! we recommend e-cars n.i (02825 652 200) or tc bros taxis (02825 644 440).

what are my accomodation options?

While there is no accommodation available at the venue, there are plenty of nearby hotels in ballymema. we recommend the galgorm resort and spa, tullyglass house hotel, leighinmohr house or the adair arms.

can i bring a plus one?

We kindly ask that only those named on your invitation attend the wedding and reception at the wooltower.

are kids invited?

While we love your little ones, we ask that only children named on your invitation are in attendance.

will it be an unplugged ceremony?

Yes, we want you to be present and in the moment so we ask that you put your phones away for our ceremony. our very talented phographer will capture all the important moments. we would also ask that all guests refrain from posting any photos from our wedding on social media until we have shared our official photos.
